#

Quick Borscht with Pre-cooked Beets

30 min
$12
150 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupQuickHealthy

Description

A vibrant and hearty Russian beet soup that’s quick to prepare and packed with flavor.

Ingredients

  • pre-cooked beets: 2 cups
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • potatoes, diced: 1 cup
  • carrots, grated: 1 cup
  • onion, chopped: 1 medium
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • fresh dill (for garnish): to taste
  • sour cream (for serving): to taste
